N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 610.7 - Disciplinary procedure

State Regulations

Disciplinary proceedings and
proceedings under section
603.16
of this Title against any
legal consultant shall be initiated and conducted in the manner and by the same
agencies as prescribed by law for disciplinary proceedings against
attorneys. Notes
